OL,6,FA man who murdered his wife before
OL,7,Fdismembering her body and paying a
OL,8,Ffriend to help dispose of the remains
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for life.
OL,11,FNicholas Metson, 28, stabbed 26-year-
OL,12,Fold Holly Bramley to death at their
OL,13,Fflat in Lincoln in March last year.
OL,15,FHe then cut her body up into more than
OL,16,F200 pieces and contacted his friend
OL,17,FJoshua Hancock, 28.
OL,19,FThe pair in the village of Bassingham
OL,20,Fabout 10 miles away.
