OL,3,CMan who cut up wife's body and paid
OL,4,Cfriend to dispose of remains sentenced
OL,6,FSome of her body parts have yet to be
OL,7,Ffound, Lincoln Crown Court heard.
OL,9,FMetson initially denied murder but
OL,10,Fchanged his plea to guilty before a
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for a minimum of 19
OL,14,Fyears 316 days.
OL,16,FHancock admitted obstructing a
OL,17,Fcoroner, along with unrelated offences
OL,18,Fof attempting sexual communication
OL,19,Fwith a child and drugs offences.
