OL,3,CMan who cut up wife's body and paid
OL,4,Cfriend to dispose of remains sentenced
OL,6,FHe was jailed for a total of three
OL,7,Fyears and three months and given a 10-
OL,8,Fyear sexual harm prevention order.
OL,10,FThe court heard Metson and Ms Bramley
OL,11,Fhad been together since 2016 and
OL,12,Fmarried in 2021.
OL,14,FBy the start of 2023, Judge Simon
OL,15,FHirst said, "the relationship had come
OL,16,Fto an end".
OL,18,FMs Bramley was last seen on 17 March
OL,19,Fon CCTV.
