OL,3,CMan who cut up wife's body and paid
OL,4,Cfriend to dispose of remains sentenced
OL,6,FIn the following days, Metson put a
OL,7,Fnote on the door of their flat saying
OL,8,Fhe was isolating due to Covid and
OL,9,Fcancelled a takeaway delivery.
OL,11,FAt some point he stabbed her then used
OL,12,Fa "variety of different tools" to
OL,13,Fdismember the body, the judge said.
OL,15,FHe kept the body parts in his flat and
OL,16,Fsent messages to people saying Ms
OL,17,FBramley had left him.
