OL,3,CMan who cut up wife's body and paid
OL,4,Cfriend to dispose of remains sentenced
OL,6,FHe made suspicious internet searches,
OL,7,Fincluding "how to dispose of a dead
OL,8,Fbody" and "can someone haunt me after
OL,9,Fthey die?".
OL,11,FHe also hacked into Ms Bramley's
OL,12,Fsocial media accounts to send messages
OL,13,Fimplying that she had left him,
OL,14,Falleging that she had assaulted him
OL,15,Fand transferring money to him by way
OL,16,Fof apology.
OL,18,FPolice were called to the couple's
OL,19,Fflat on 24 March after concerns were
OL,20,Fraised for Ms Bramley's safety.
