OL,6,FOfficers visited the following day but
OL,7,Fgot no response on the first two
OL,8,Foccasions they knocked at the door.
OL,10,FWhen Metson answered after their third
OL,11,Fattempt, he claimed not to know where
OL,12,Fhis wife was and said she had suffered
OL,13,Fmental health problems, self-harmed
OL,14,Fand subjected him to domestic abuse.
OL,16,FAn initial search of the flat revealed
OL,17,Fa strong smell of ammonia, blood-
OL,18,Fstained sheets and a saw.
