OL,3,CMan who cut up wife's body and paid
OL,4,Cfriend to dispose of remains sentenced
OL,6,FAfter Metson was arrested, members of
OL,7,Fthe public found some of her body
OL,8,Fparts in carrier bags.
OL,10,FBut some of the body, including parts
OL,11,Fof her heart, lungs, ribs and fingers
OL,12,Fare still missing.
OL,14,FIn a statement given at a previous
OL,15,Fhearing,
OL,17,FJudge Hirts told Metson: "Holly's
OL,18,Ffamily and friends will never know how
OL,19,Fand why she was killed."
OL,21,F'Our hearts are broken'
