OL,3,CMan who cut up wife's body and paid
OL,4,Cfriend to dispose of remains sentenced
OL,6,FSpeaking outside court, Ms Bramley's
OL,7,Ffamily spoke of the loss of their
OL,8,F"vibrant, happy and affectionate
OL,9,Fdaughter, sister and auntie in such a
OL,10,Fbarbaric, heinous and violent way".
OL,12,FHer sister Sarah-Jayne Lindop said:
OL,13,F"Today is by no means closure, but it
OL,14,Fis a milestone in the process of our
OL,15,Fgrief and healing."
OL,17,FShe spoke of Ms Bramley's love of
OL,18,Fsinging dancing and her passion for
OL,19,Fanimals.
