OL,3,CMan who cut up wife's body and paid
OL,4,Cfriend to dispose of remains sentenced
OL,6,FShe said she was "rarely seen without
OL,7,Fa smile on her face".
OL,9,F"She adored her younger brothers,
OL,10,Fnieces and nephews and wanted nothing
OL,11,Fmore than to become a mother herself
OL,12,Fone day," she said.
OL,14,F"Sadly meeting the man who cruelly
OL,15,Ftook her life was just the beginning
OL,16,Fof a rocky road for Holly as she
OL,17,Fembarked on a life of domestic abuse
OL,18,Fand despite our trying as a family we
OL,19,Fnever managed to save her from that.
