OL,6,F"We miss Holly so much our hearts are
OL,7,Fbroken. But, if anything, we need her
OL,8,Fdeath to highlight that domestic abuse
OL,9,Fis not okay. If she had recognised
OL,10,Fthat this was what she was being
OL,11,Fsubjected to, we may have her home
OL,12,Fwith us now."
OL,14,FShe urged other victims of abuse to
OL,15,Fseek support.
